name: Thing 2
description:
Introduction

A short WCC canyon featuring 5 rappels up to 90'. Retrievable anchor can be used for all 5 rappels, or bring extra webbing. This can be combined with Thing 1 for a half day adventure.

Approach

Descent

5 rappels under 90'.

Exit

Exit up main gully/ drainage between Thing 1 and Thing 2.
